BT 1 0 0 1 0 134 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (To reinforce the efficacy of our proposed Generative Engine Optimization methods, we evaluate) Tj T* (them on Perplexity.ai, a real deployed Generative Engine with a large user base. Results are in) Tj T* (Table 5. Similar to our generative engine, Quotation Addition performs best in Position-Adjusted) Tj T* (Word Count with a $2 2 \\%$ improvement over the baseline. Methods that performed well in our) Tj T* (generative engine such as Cite Sources, Statistics Addition show improvements of up to $9 \\%$) Tj T* (and $3 7 \\%$ on the two metrics. Our observations, such as the ineffectiveness of traditional SEO) Tj T* (methods like Keyword Stuffing, are further highlighted, as it performs $1 0 \\%$ worse than the) Tj T* (baseline. The results are significant for three reasons: 1\) they underscore the importance of) Tj T* (developing different Generative Engine Optimization methods to benefit content creators, 2\) they) Tj T* (highlight the generalizability of our proposed GEO methods on different generative engines, 3\) they) Tj T* (demonstrate that content creators can use our easy-to-implement proposed GEO methods directly,) Tj T* (thus having a high real-world impact. We refer readers to Appendix C.1 for more details.) Tj T* ET
