BT 1 0 0 1 0 98 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (Evidence-based Answer Generation: Previous works have used several techniques for answer) Tj T* (generation backed by sources. Nakano et al. [19] trained GPT-3 to navigate web environments to) Tj T* (generate source-backed answers. Similarly, other methods [17, 23, 24] fetch sources via search) Tj T* (engines for answer generation. Our work unifies these approaches and provides a common) Tj T* (benchmark for improving these systems in the future. In a recent working draft, Kumar and) Tj T* (Lakkaraju [11] showed that strategic text sequences can manipulate LLM recommendations to) Tj T* (enhance product visibility in generative engines. While their approach focuses on increasing) Tj T* (product visibility through adversarial text, our method introduces non-adversarial strategies to) Tj T* (optimize any website content for improved visibility in generative engine search results.) Tj T* ET
