BT 1 0 0 1 0 74 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (Retrieval-Augmented Language Models: Several recent works have tackled the issues of limited) Tj T* (memory of language models by fetching relevant sources from a knowledge base to complete a) Tj T* (task [3, 9, 18]. However, Generative Engine needs to generate an answer and provide attributions) Tj T* (throughout the answer. Further, Generative Engine is not limited to a single text modality regarding) Tj T* (both input and output. Additionally, the framework of Generative Engine is not limited to fetching) Tj T* (relevant sources but instead comprises multiple tasks such as query reformulation, source) Tj T* (selection, and making decisions on how and when to perform them.) Tj T* ET
